//**********************************************************************
*
*                   SETUP
*
***********************************************************************//

Install pip
  https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/

Install and set up virtualenv
  https://virtualenv.pypa.io/en/stable/

Clone the project
    git clone https://github.com/schmidtvl/hackbot.git

  1. Set up the virtualenv in env/ under root directory of project
          mkdir env
          virtualenv env

  2. Activate the virtual env
          source bin/env/activate

  3. Install the slackclient
          pip install slackclient
